name: AmourShield - Integration w OurTime + TD
description:
Made for Western's Product Design Sprint


Essentially our creation was an addition to banking apps and senior's dating sites to try and mitigate scams by protecting users - so some of the pages were directly taken from those sites ( and then we added our design onto it )


This was my second formal attempt at designing smth ;0

I worked with another beginner UX designer to make this!
